headline: Skyworks Unveils Industry’s First Clocks for Ethernet and PCI Express® With 18fs RMS Phase Jitter
summary: IRVINE, Calif., June 25, 2025--Skyworks Solutions, Inc. (Nasdaq: SWKS), an innovator of high-performance analog and mixed-signal semiconductors connecting people, places and things, today announced its latest timing products, the SKY63104/5/6 family of jitter attenuating clocks and the SKY62101 ultra-low jitter clock generator. Based on Skyworks’ fifth generation DSPLL® and MultiSynth™ technologies, these devices enable any-frequency, any-output clock generation and single-IC clock tree solution
